ic/shygirl-cancels-co-headline-tour-with-tinashe-due-to-illness-3518988">推迟与 Tinashe 的美国巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-drops-ravey-new-single-fke-featuring-kingdom-listen-3561739">聆听 Shygirl 与 Kingdom 合作的热门新单曲“f@k€”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
